  "curation": {
    "synopsis": "Khemet, a disgraced Triarch Praetorian, has endured a Necron punishment worse than death: conscious imprisonment for a failure that may not be hers alone. Lord Hekasun offers her one chance to restore her honour by awakening Orymous, a tomb world now paved over and occupied by the Astra Militarum. To complete the mission she must slip between Imperial defences, buried Necron systems, and Hekasun's own dynastic designs. A cold redemption-thriller where immortal pride meets the practical problem of humans living on top of your grave.",
